{"blocks":[{"key":"9f4no","text":"Randomly pick five carriers out from culturing flask and put into a 50 mL centrifuge tube. {"blocks":[{"key":"2sgsm","text":"Use a dropper, add 2-3 mL 1X PBS into the Washing tube. Cap the tube and rinse every corner of the inside wall of tube using the PBS added by rotating the tube.
